Items.c: <[>可惜我不熟影子內衛之事,心有疑慮,不敢冒然與她同行共事。<]>
Items.mt: <[>It is a pity that I am not familiar with the affairs of the shadow inner guards, and I have doubts, so I dare not venture to go with her to work together. <]>
